in wallet 1.1:
  + (1) new program creation shall save the previous databases as history, and create current databases from scratch.
  (2) programs shall be created with limits according to tags.
  + (3) irregular tcp messages shall be handled without crash.
  + (4) status report shall be emitted from a new port.
  (5) records with null tags shall be automatically cleaned.
  (6) scheduler class shall be developed with minimum functionality.
  (7) programs shall have specified "excluded" tags, which will not affect records thereof.
